1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,870
Most sales teams do not have a process

2
00:00:01,900 --> 00:00:02,260
problem.

3
00:00:02,820 --> 00:00:04,430
They have an execution problem.

4
00:00:04,990 --> 00:00:06,460
The process is documented.

5
00:00:07,010 --> 00:00:08,240
The stages are defined.

6
00:00:08,740 --> 00:00:10,460
The criteria are written down.

7
00:00:10,670 --> 00:00:12,690
But what actually happens in deals looks

8
00:00:12,780 --> 00:00:13,990
nothing like the process.

9
00:00:14,710 --> 00:00:15,870
Discovery gets skipped.

10
00:00:16,460 --> 00:00:17,760
Qualification is assumed.

11
00:00:18,390 --> 00:00:19,980
Champions are never confirmed.

12
00:00:20,460 --> 00:00:21,920
The process exists on paper.

13
00:00:22,510 --> 00:00:23,990
Execution happens in the field.

14
00:00:24,660 --> 00:00:26,940
AI closes this gap by making the process

15
00:00:26,980 --> 00:00:28,210
visible in real time.

16
00:00:28,780 --> 00:00:30,800
Not by auditing calls after the fact.

17
00:00:31,430 --> 00:00:33,250
By surfacing gaps while there is still

18
00:00:33,310 --> 00:00:34,080
time to act.

19
00:00:34,700 --> 00:00:36,750
Which deals moved to proposal without a

20
00:00:36,800 --> 00:00:38,060
confirmed problem statement.

21
00:00:38,620 --> 00:00:40,220
Which opportunities have no executive

22
00:00:40,250 --> 00:00:41,510
contact after thirty days.

23
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:43,940
Which accounts have gone dark and need

24
00:00:43,990 --> 00:00:44,570
intervention.

25
00:00:45,170 --> 00:00:46,790
The goal is not a better process.

26
00:00:47,180 --> 00:00:48,690
The goal is a process that actually

27
00:00:48,760 --> 00:00:49,140
runs.

28
00:00:49,290 --> 00:00:50,700
Follow A-Gent to build it.
